{"tid":2352451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家好似開始淡忘","createTime":"2021-01-04T04:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T17:50:29.000Z","uid":173530,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4c24e412c3c76285961ec9d4929445556f993403","tid":2352451,"uid":173530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:51:59.000Z","msg":"個個大大聲講自己係邊到淘寶返嚟<br />\n會有人附和、討論、link<br />\n<br />\n有人問、你返工返咁遠車費咪好乸利囉<br />\n我話綠卡，啲人就窒咗窒<br />\n：哦～咁就慳咗唔少<br />\n<br />\n身邊好似再冇人用綠卡<br />\n堅持用綠卡，但係人地眼中好似係為咗慳錢<br />\n有時都覺得自己係異類，甚至諗，我係咪應該棄用<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己開始被同化，人都開始淡忘初衷<br />\n我知係無可避免<br />\n只係覺得好唏噓"},{"pid":"a2edf2b8184b172120706a982305de20c17791ba","tid":2352451,"uid":173530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d410f0bbbc0aee15eb132919fa49a266194752","tid":2352451,"uid":187489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知可以點<br />\n希望可以堅持到"},{"pid":"e46febf23d67c203882fb686c42ec214db0f3f3b","tid":2352451,"uid":173530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:56:08.000Z","msg":"喬映瑜家屬委托律師盧思位遭四川省司法廳吊銷律師執照<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2352345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2352345</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d2512e549501a5ace09a3c2e42bbddfdb71327c9","tid":2352451,"uid":45007,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"老實講 我到依一刻都無用過綠卡<br />\n你唔鐘意黨鐵咪唔好坐<br />\n合理化自己坐黨鐵比2蚊為咩<br />\n<br />\n利申 如非必要唔會坐黨鐵"},{"pid":"a45859b078729768784c6e0fff6f1bb85f8f5c9f","tid":2352451,"uid":17